{"tid":784604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典工作假期實錄+你問我答","createTime":"2018-08-18T13:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T07:34:42.000Z","uid":63132,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a59022fb94236e6c6f1f7b47a60a354f7eaf167c","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"（借ac po)<br />\n見到新聞有報+fb有page講開<br />\n大家有唔同立場，到大家接收到嘅資訊可能有扭曲左，咁我都分享少少第一身嘅經驗啦。<br />\n<br />\n竹6月到瑞典，8月申請到personal number，之後先可以再申請銀行戶口。<br />\n老實講係呢邊嘅人大部份都已經用咗唔同嘅方法解決「所謂既問題」，講出嚟純粹係想政府修補漏洞，同埋提醒之後打算嚟嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n整各樣証件就度度都要嘅<br />\n喺呢度我就集中講申請稅號嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n想申請用作交稅嘅「稅號」有兩種：<br />\n一：Personal number (包含人口資料，可享福利，可用作交稅）只要你逗留瑞典達一年或以上就可申請<br />\n<br />\n二：Co-ordination number（只用作交稅），只要有工作就可申請<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常見問題一：持working holiday visa嘅香港人是否符合資格申請personal Number？<br />\n<br />\n答：瑞典官方回應不統一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有回應指personal Number係唔會批俾持有workig holiday Visa嘅人；亦有唔獲批嘅人得到回覆話，因為起簽證開始嘅日期之後先進入瑞典，所以逗留喺瑞典唔夠365日因此唔會批。<br />\n據瑞典駐香港領事館嘅說法，瑞典係唔會批personal number比持有working holiday visa嘅人。問題係兩邊各有說法，而係瑞典申請personal number成功同失敗嘅個案參半，亦睇唔到所謂嘅批核標準。<br />\n<br />\n常見問題二：申請Co-ordination number程序<br />\n答：需要先找到工作，然後帶着工作合約到Tax Office申請。困難在於當地人以及僱主都唔熟悉Co-ordination number，大至zara等公司都唔肯聘請冇personal number嘅人，亦都唔肯先同你簽約比你申請co-ordination number。<br />\n冇工作&gt;冇number&gt;冇工作<br />\n<br />\n常見問題三：瑞典人做嘢效率極低，除左慢仲好19，你整張permit卡正常一星期收到。當你三星期仲未收到去問職員，職員會叫你去報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> What?去報警？你知唔知自己講緊咩？同類既19野太多太多...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實第一年開，大家都冇攻略話要點樣做。<br />\n第一年就過尼嘅人都係開荒牛，就好似打機唔睇攻略咁，又有另一種快感。<br />\n我好彩喺呢度搵到個絲打，入咗個group，大家一樣處境可以互相交流得到嘅資訊。<br />\n官方話你銀行存款需要有15000瑞典克朗（大約港紙13000），但其實一個月租金加按金已經差唔多冇晒，所以要預備多啲錢（無論係信用卡銀行卡定現金），要留意瑞典至今仲未有支援銀聯嘅櫃員機。<br />\n<br />\n你問我點解咁慘都仲留起度唔番香港？<br />\n我覺得一生人冇咩咁既機會可以出走，都需要d衝動先成事，過到嚟亦唔想輕易放棄，最多最壞打算都係買機票返香港，冇咩可以輸。<br />\n呢邊嘅工種不外乎sushi bar，精品鋪，hostel。其實working holiday都係想又work下又holiday下，賺夠錢就走。同埋生活又係同香港完全唔同，體驗下唔同既生活方式都冇壞既。<br />\n睇到起新聞下面留言嘅人，真係想講唔該積下口德啦。<br />\n<br />\n有咩問題可以起度問，未必答到你，答到盡量答。"},{"pid":"95912e5d237e11e68c5755ffc2e335b09b3eaf93","tid":784604,"uid":11896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"有無限你只可以搵咩工種"},{"pid":"b7c63e7215726e079e86a4146c986cba4e915903","tid":784604,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"搵工/住宿有乜難處?"},{"pid":"1c04126ee6be7462f665e849ac2bd2b604c0aa32","tid":784604,"uid":79303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"感覺如何 自己翻緊瑞典公司 佢地都話瑞典無咩野好做 <br />\n生活指數高唔高 人工幾多 食租大約幾多 工時幾長<br />\n<br />\n係香港做到悶 想出走下"},{"pid":"dcf9d3b7d9f78a9e16ebb648393211889819b47a","tid":784604,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"知過咩野工"},{"pid":"58ddfee6f9afff042d4963e5a0a470753f3b139e","tid":784604,"uid":99978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:01:35.000Z","msg":"如果識swedish<br />\n係咪好多工都揾到？"},{"pid":"acf4ffff40246c396edb58fc617cdf10578e8e36","tid":784604,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"136b058e84f8acd477fd7b4b30253bd261523582","tid":784604,"uid":56661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"剩係去過斯德哥爾摩， 啲餐廳好貴， 全部都1xx~2xx港紙一餐<br />\n<br />\n得姨媽傢俬啲肉丸熱狗雪糕最平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n39, 49, 59 SEK =&gt; 8, 12, 16 粒肉丸<br />\n<br />\n1 SEK = 0.86 HKD<br />\n<br />\n快餐店都6x ~ 7x蚊<br />\n除非食最平嘅飽，就1x ~ 20蚊1個"},{"pid":"01dbd764dc67f0dd79afcfedcc7ebbc434162cbb","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95912e5d237e11e68c5755ffc2e335b09b3eaf93","tid":784604,"uid":11896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:51:33.000Z","msg":"有無限你只可以搵咩工種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:05:46.000Z","msg":"冇 只要有人請你"},{"pid":"55b308c82e564ec77fe96fa9cc8cef638663ded0","tid":784604,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:21:50.000Z","msg":"en唔enjoy?<br />\n同你出發前既想像有無咩唔同"},{"pid":"b56c46c08d66274fb9a3f5797f244074137d730a","tid":784604,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:25:02.000Z","msg":"多唔多台灣同志"},{"pid":"6a4b4713c49dfe7e85abdf680e07e3938c08fe15","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b7c63e7215726e079e86a4146c986cba4e915903","tid":784604,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"搵工/住宿有乜難處?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:30:49.000Z","msg":"搵工：港人唔識瑞典文，但識英文廣東話普通話，已經好過好多唔識英文既人，起碼唔限制於做廚房，但係證件上比較麻煩，工作機會我覺得唔算多，所以都比較難搵工。瑞典人英文好好，溝通唔成問題，做下sales，餐廳係冇問題。但有得揀既話僱主當然會想請番識瑞典文既人，尼邊唔少移民難民，都識講瑞典文，仲有東歐、大陸等各地工簽尼既人，我地搵工既market可以話一樣。加上CN需要有工作先申請到，其實我覺得申請工作假期簽證個意義冇左。<br />\n搵工方法都係walk in入鋪頭問請唔請，同埋wechat group，但聽講大部分都係打華人工，offer一定冇咁靚，亦有黑工。<br />\n<br />\n住宿方面：stockholm尼講都幾緊張，local既網都幾難搵房源，通常上wechat華人group有大陸人同香港人放租。一間房放租或同人合租都有，主要留意番治安問題。普遍地鐵各條線尾站治安都比較差。"},{"pid":"ed206a77940ab83039cd61792a0f6d0ed96c5145","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c04126ee6be7462f665e849ac2bd2b604c0aa32","tid":784604,"uid":79303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:54:21.000Z","msg":"感覺如何 自己翻緊瑞典公司 佢地都話瑞典無咩野好做 <br />\n生活指數高唔高 人工幾多 食租大約幾多 工時幾長<br />\n<br />\n係香港做到悶 想出走下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:43:47.000Z","msg":"生活其實幾舒服，食好住好，冇香港生活節奏咁快，stockholm市中心算多人，其實有d似香港，住宅地區係舒服既，買野我又真係覺得唔貴，出街食下飯既話百幾蚊，唔出街日日自己煮，有穩定收入既話完全負擔到。<br />\n人工好睇搵到咩工，唔多聽到人真係搵到full time，有d可能一日幾個鐘，有d就一星期幾日，睇你彩數。一個月搵到幾千蚊（夠交租同買餸食飯同搭車）就唔難過，搵唔到工或者有工但等勁耐未出到糧就好頭痕。<br />\n<br />\n租一人2500-4500克朗都有，睇你要求（港紙對克朗大約1:1.1）<br />\n食睇你點食，番餐廳可以三餐都唔洗錢，自己煮一個月都唔洗1000<br />\n<br />\n工時唔定，睇咩工"},{"pid":"2c5bbe66256af80a562dd96905863bb5d25d6fb8","tid":784604,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:51:55.000Z","msg":"都幾勁，開初都想申請，後尾見到關於稅務同埋銀行野根本無配合到政府呢個計劃，所以卻步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c19240b6ef34f26b309767de16933b15b691c3","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55b308c82e564ec77fe96fa9cc8cef638663ded0","tid":784604,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:21:50.000Z","msg":"en唔enjoy?<br />\n同你出發前既想像有無咩唔同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:53:34.000Z","msg":"好難話好enjoy，好多做緊野既都仲等緊稅號/糧，成日好似今日唔知聽日事咁，瑞典政府做野又19。有朋友一直收唔到residence card，去問職員，職員竟然叫佢去報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩既人有班人一樣處境可以大家一齊呻下<br />\n<br />\n出發前唸住會有d短期性質，唔係咁似番工既工，例如馬場農場<br />\n但發現馬場農場係有既，但唔請人。一係請農場工既email address係唔vaild既，咁馬死落地行，都要做其他工。<br />\n瑞典真係唔少難民，有時都驚驚地。"},{"pid":"67acef59a2a947e7ed64ed42634613e577646df6","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcf9d3b7d9f78a9e16ebb648393211889819b47a","tid":784604,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"知過咩野工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:54:23.000Z","msg":"餐館"},{"pid":"e380e98711ab190f480b58e82a3df5968a647fff","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b56c46c08d66274fb9a3f5797f244074137d730a","tid":784604,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:25:02.000Z","msg":"多唔多台灣同志"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T20:55:10.000Z","msg":"冇見過，見過唔少大陸蒙古東歐"},{"pid":"76e64526d922f5019595f2eac847c99b0061a807","tid":784604,"uid":27833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T21:15:12.000Z","msg":"加油! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你喺Stockholm嘅話, 得閒出嚟fika! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7376104618b8d4dfdbfe8145c6cc98711f5057db","tid":784604,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T21:16:51.000Z","msg":"普遍人工幾錢左右"},{"pid":"608579c3c40ed8705ca1fb144ab650a60bea051f","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76e64526d922f5019595f2eac847c99b0061a807","tid":784604,"uid":27833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T21:15:12.000Z","msg":"加油! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你喺Stockholm嘅話, 得閒出嚟fika! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T22:38:27.000Z","msg":"Ok wo 巴打讀緊書定移左民？"},{"pid":"b7857659d86eb0f365c210926a0de2e91a7655a3","tid":784604,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7376104618b8d4dfdbfe8145c6cc98711f5057db","tid":784604,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T21:16:51.000Z","msg":"普遍人工幾錢左右"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T22:44:04.000Z","msg":"好難講普遍<br />\n正正常常基本1xx一個鐘稅前，扣完收入同香港差唔多<br />\n華人工既幾低都有，但佢賣點就係幫人搞工簽幫你移民過尼"},{"pid":"d38e18b4664d24eb3708670b92aeca7b9fcef1b3","tid":784604,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T22:51:32.000Z","msg":"倫敦working holiday 緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢到都唔易搵工，不過好彩2個人一齊過來開支有得share，2份糧收入幾可觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5a757af12d265264bba275b6392d2123b304d9","tid":784604,"uid":99978,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:00:56.000Z","msg":"係外國仲要痴中國人埋堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分分係間諜群組來"},{"pid":"bf6881845af3e808f6502f4a0aa54f4c6164acad","tid":784604,"uid":34222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"瑞典交流完半年<br />\n<br />\nHejhej<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> vad heter du"},{"pid":"38ee252634d8fdc0c42669a70770457181df2934","tid":784604,"uid":101909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"華人既工係做D乜多?"}]}